        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Securing America's Clean Fuels Infrastructure</b></p> <p>This bill extends the tax credit for alternative fuel vehicle refueling property through 2029. It also increases the allowable amount of such credit from $30,000 to $200,000 for any single item of refueling property.</p>]]>
        </text>
